post.title: Start over
post.body:
I just finished the outline of a chapter in the future new edition of my supervisor's textbook.

Before that I was fighting with my colleague's terrible php code, which was copied directly from another project, causing lots of errors. It hasn't worked yet.

I got up late this morning and due to the shower I had to stay in the dorm, trying to build zeronet for a second time.

I lost the key to my previous zeroid and sites, but actually nothing was left there.
